    <div class="tip"><span style="flex-shrink:0">🌸</span><div><strong>Lehenga pehle chunein, theme baad mein</strong> — Most couples yeh ulta karte hain! Pehle bridal lehenga finalize karo — phir uska color palette theme decide karega. Clash avoid ho jaata hai automatically.</div></div>
    <div class="tip"><span style="flex-shrink:0">💡</span><div><strong>Lighting sabse bada impact deta hai</strong> — ₹50,000 ke flowers + ₹15,000 ki lighting se behtar hai ₹20,000 ke flowers + ₹45,000 ki premium lighting. Warm fairy lights ne average venues ko magical bana diya hai.</div></div>
    <div class="tip"><span style="flex-shrink:0">📅</span><div><strong>Season ke saath theme match karo</strong> — Summer mein dark maroon theme mein guests uncomfortable hote hain. Winter mein pastels washed out lagte hain. Season + theme + venue — teen cheezein ek saath sochni chahiye.</div></div>
    <div class="tip"><span style="flex-shrink:0">🌼</span><div><strong>Local flowers 5x saste hote hain</strong> — Imported orchids ke peeche mat bhaago. Genda phool, roses, tuberose, mogra — Indian flowers sabse impactful hain aur 80% saste. Seasonal flowers double attractive lagte hain.</div></div>
    <div class="tip"><span style="flex-shrink:0">📸</span><div><strong>Photography ke liye theme consider karo</strong> — White backdrop + dark lehenga = stunning. Dark venue + dark lehenga = lost. AI-generated color palette photographer ko share karo — woh accordingly lighting set karenge.</div></div>
    <div class="tip"><span style="flex-shrink:0">👗</span><div><strong>Family color coordination theme ka hissa hai</strong> — Groom ki family ka color, bride ki family ka color — yeh plan karo pehle. Group photos mein coordinated colors magical lagte hain. AI se outfit coordination section copy karo — family ko bhejo.</div></div>
